{"tid":1606882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"齊上齊落 各位記住 聽日唔係end game","createTime":"2019-09-30T16:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T02:11:35.000Z","uid":18577,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9fddc5a89fe99fa69ffda8815131be8340895860","tid":1606882,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:23:13.000Z","msg":"聽日係港殤日<br />\n但唔代表聽日係end game<br />\n請各位好好保重<br />\n唔好有唔係你死就我亡嘅心態<br />\n我地唔會想有任何手足任何真香港人有事<br />\n<br />\n記住我地要係煲底下除口罩<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係一定要等到天崎出黎個日<br />\n<br />\n所以請大家依刻上Facebook 打status <br />\n或者Send個msg比一個你信得佢過嘅人聽<br />\n話比佢知你熱愛生命熱愛香港<br />\n唔會做出自殺行為<br />\n<br />\n我地一定會等到香港重光個日<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"62835879ff4786ab43e556deafae0089c1cc359d","tid":1606882,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:24:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"e0271c856c600c6543ce23dc4c52c4aca9d0d620","tid":1606882,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:26:47.000Z","msg":"一個不能少呀"},{"pid":"ec6362acdfadf77c2327ceeb464d405ea7400fc0","tid":1606882,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:29:44.000Z","msg":"轉載：<br />\n重點通知，明天10.1 魔警會有可能發射實彈，以下是魔警重點防守區域；<br />\n1. 港島銅鑼灣至西環，重兵集中在上環/警總和北角警署用作包圍。<br />\n2. 九龍在深水埗和太子，重兵在荔枝角/九龍灣和尖沙咀警署用作包圍。<br />\n3. 新界在沙田/葵芳和將軍澳，重兵在火炭/大埔/荃灣和將軍澳工業村用作包圍。<br />\n<br />\n至於元朗/天水圍/屯門/北角和炮台山則由各自的黑社會負責。<br />\n<br />\n而共軍則會混入各個魔警防守區，MTR 會配合封站。<br />\n<br />\n淋病及一眾賣港賊北上是為自己制造不知情/不參與的證據，亦表示明天魔警和共軍可以大開殺戒，以香港市民的血祭共匪10.1。<br />\n<br />\n由於明天是假期，我和分析員在此先祝大家平安和快樂渡過。請記住行街時一定要帶長鐵遮/扇/蒸餾水/冰水/兩件淺色備用t-shirt/四至六條毛巾/豬嘴/眼罩/尿袋和多些硬幣坐巴士（盡量避免MTR），長鐵遮和扇可以用來私了/自衛。<br />\n<br />\n暫時監聽到魔警和共軍的步署係咁多，會keep 住update if they change their plan。<br />\n<br />\n明天多區教堂會全日開放。各位請事前計畫好撤退路線（plan A &amp; B &amp; C 路線）。<br />\n<br />\n剛剛收到消息，各區的體育館/民政署和社區中心已經被魔警徵用，當中會用來給共軍進駐及暫時收押被捕人士。<br />\n<br />\n分析員提意大家明天行到興的時候便去各大戲院睇戲 or 商場涼冷氣以免中暑。<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳。"},{"pid":"86c84ae5e0044e631e7145f7c81f4396547b7de8","tid":1606882,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a66ce056e5596750eb5b68a35715b974e40bfd","tid":1606882,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aaa0f6115a4fec36b7cc9074764fa4ba8921a5c","tid":1606882,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa0833d6a3e435c8d661e5183fd713381d8045c","tid":1606882,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5a21aa9de35dfc2c395bc07de48f52ba165574","tid":1606882,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:16:00.000Z","msg":"香港要人！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97206dbcdbde657099f488b6b4f139ce913d8d5f","tid":1606882,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b5a21aa9de35dfc2c395bc07de48f52ba165574","tid":1606882,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:16:00.000Z","msg":"香港要人！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T17:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69b133220de585ca4f8e385bc12467394742a02","tid":1606882,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:25:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd69688dd2326e8924b0ca2a15ce521549eb20a","tid":1606882,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:27:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"457b4493807c9ca412d5af3fc2dccac473fd1fed","tid":1606882,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"952bcb9dd25b984782b535bd4b772bf11284958b","tid":1606882,"uid":289191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T01:51:18.000Z","msg":"習近平老羞成怒<br />\n國慶日血流成河<br />\n佢唔會CARE<br />\n佢會覺得自己勁過鄧小平<br />\n佢會覺得自己媲美毛澤東<br />\n歷史選擇了香港<br />\n大家與有榮焉<br />\n習近平要炒香港<br />\n我咃有得揀咩?"},{"pid":"e18c672a6d9ca626635dd21388c3f924101a0b99","tid":1606882,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8938bea3c0596af9f963fc09b5b0cd6b63d2f7","tid":1606882,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dee5605c3e69d0bbb0ee3fa527ee9e4d9dfccb0","tid":1606882,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ea811ceafab04cba84cf8b1dded9e9562addd1","tid":1606882,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:11:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4466ef5fb85c7cdd71ce6309158732bfd29efdb5","tid":1606882,"uid":269363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:11:35.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}